https://staging.validation.linaro.org/static/docs/v2/support.html

Reporting Bugs
==============

All bugs should be reported to Linaro at - 
https://bugs.linaro.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=LAVA%20Framework

LAVA features are planned using JIRA:
https://projects.linaro.org/projects/LAVA

